<h3 id="for_statement">For Statement</h3>
<p>For statements allow you to continually output some text for every element
  in a list. Here's what for statements look like:</p>
  
<pre>
  &lt;ol&gt;
  {{ "{% for error in errors %}" }}
    &lt;li&gt;{{ "{{ error }}" }}&lt;/li&gt;
  {{ "{% endfor %}" }}
  &lt;/ol&gt;
</pre>